# RAG Chat Storage - Backend (Spring Boot)

## Quick start (dev)
1. Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and update values.
2. Build & run with Docker Compose:
3. Backend will be available at http://localhost:8080
- Health: http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health
- Adminer (DB browser): http://localhost:8081

## API Key authentication

All non-whitelisted endpoints require a header:

    X-API-KEY: StrongKey@Dev

Set the key in environment variable `API_KEY`, or use `security.apikey.keys` in `application.yml` for comma-separated keys. Example `.env`:

    API_KEY=StrongKey@Dev

Whitelisted endpoints (accessible without key): `/api/v1/health`, `/swagger-ui/**`, `/v3/api-docs/**`.
